{"tid":1297968,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【好片分享】Red and Black Song 致感到疲憊、灰心嘅戰友","createTime":"2019-07-08T17:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T18:59:26.000Z","uid":2010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"143e4e60713bc127db5764d0a105eb5295c20e25","tid":1297968,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"喺過去嘅一個月，香港真係發生咗好多事，好多人感到氣餒，又會覺得無晒方向。<br />\n呢段繃緊嘅時間，除咗可以靠一時嘅玩樂去放鬆，<br />\n亦可以睇下一啲振奮人心嘅片段，去維持自己嘅意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講起《孤星淚》電影，總會諗到〈Do You Hear the People Sing〉，<br />\n而我就經常會聽＋睇另一首〈Red and Black Song〉，去鼓勵同提醒自己。<br />\n趁住空閒，同大家分享一下，順便摘錄幾段歌詞，同埋劣譯幾句（有錯請指正）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cjp-Gyo5tNM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fcjp-Gyo5tNM&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUv7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=08642ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cjp-Gyo5tNM</a><br />\n<strong>It is time for us all <br />\nTo decide who we are</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">而家我哋必須決定，自己將要成為點樣嘅人。</span><br />\n<strong>Do we fight for the right<br />\nTo a night at the opera now?</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋嘅抗爭，係咪為咗一刻嘅聲色享樂？</span><br />\n<strong>Have you asked of yourselves<br />\nWhat's the price you might pay?</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你哋有冇問過自己，將要付出啲咩代價？</span><br />\n<strong>Is this simply a game<br />\nFor a rich young boy to play?</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔通革命只係富家子弟嘅遊戲？</span><br />\n<strong>The colours of the world<br />\nAre changing day by day</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋嘅周遭，每一日都風雲色變。</span><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<strong>But now there is a higher call.</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">而家有更崇高嘅使命等緊我哋</span><br />\n<strong>Who cares about your lonely soul?</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">冇人會在乎你孤單弱小嘅靈魂。</span><br />\n<strong>We strive towards a larger goal</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋正在為更偉大嘅目標搏鬥，</span><br />\n<strong>Our little lives don't count at all!</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">就連我哋條命，都不及呢個使命重要！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢條片、呢首歌唔算得係啲咩極具內涵嘅作品，<br />\n但希望有緣睇到呢度嘅你，感受到我嘅一份小小心意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，爭氣，加油！</span><br />\n（早啲休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"8135b57fdc5e142474a1a8336843cb119b3e09cf","tid":1297968,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb48faf8e8e2dd89f3171b1ca52211da7d09f354","tid":1297968,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d457234408bac8005b09cb760f548c5a4c3178","tid":1297968,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:59:26.000Z","msg":"瞓前一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}